{{Databox|fr=Azilal}}Tga '''Azilal''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: ⴰⵣⵉⵍⴰⵍ, s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: أزيلال) yat tiɣrmt illan ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]] ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Bni Mllal-Xnifra|Bni Mllal-Xnifra]] ɣ tmnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Azilal|Azilal]], d nttat ad igan tamaẓunt n tmnaḍt. Zdɣn gis kra n 44 841 umzdaɣ.

== Tarakalt ==
Tlla Azilal ɣ ammas n idrarn n [[Aṭlas mqqurn|waṭlas mqqurn]], ɣ yat tattuyt n 1 351 <abbr>m. Imsidag irakaln nns gan tn: [https://www.google.com/maps/place/Azilal/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0xda49a8b15b82733:0x233c01288788e8d8?sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjfwPDC84_xAhWMSsAKHY1pB54Q8gEwIHoECEIQAQ 31° 57′ 51″ N, 6° 34′ 27″ O]</abbr>

== Imzdaɣ ==
Ar ittini usidn lli ittuyskar ɣ usggwas n 2014 mas tiɣrmt ad zdɣn gis uggar n 44 841 n middn. Akk imzdaɣn n tiɣrmt ad gan [[imaziɣn]], ar sawaln akk gratsn s [[tutlayin timaziɣin n waṭlas]] (75.8% ar sawaln tutlayt [[Tutlayt Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas anammas|tamaziɣt n waṭlas anammas]] d 11% ar sawaln tutlayt [[Tutlayt Taclḥit|taclḥit]])<ref name=":0">[http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/ RGPH 2014 - Site HCP]</ref>.

== Asnmkta ==
Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2014 mas<ref name=":0" />:

=== Aslmd ===

* Tigmiḍi n taqubbanit (middn lli ur ssin ad aqran wala ad ttaran) : 27,4%
* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli iɣran ar usinan n usmdi nɣd uggar : 21,2%

=== Tadamsa ===

* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli llan ɣ isggasn nnsn n twuri : 40,5%
* Tigmiḍi n tarwuri (middn lli ur ṭṭafn tawuri) : 14,8%
* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli swurin dar lmxzn (nɣ kantin swurin gis) : 27,9%
* Tigmiḍi n imzdaɣ lli swurin ɣ uslig (nɣ kantin swurin gis) : 38,3%

